{"tid":1082862,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【5月播最後一集】《The Big Bang Theory》拍到276集 登電視史最長壽多鏡喜劇","createTime":"2019-03-29T08:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T08:25:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"27d6fe2c1a7deeeb2a75638f42ff52ee7ab4934d","tid":1082862,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"人氣美劇《囧男大爆炸》（The Big Bang Theory）播到第12季，近年穩坐美國收視冠軍，劇集5月播出最後一集後就正式完結，近日大破新紀錄。《囧男大爆炸》主角之一的Kaley Cuoco昨日於IG上載一張拍攝現場的大合照，相中可見劇組在現場慶祝拍到第276集，她留言確認劇集榮登當地電視史歷來最長壽多鏡拍攝處境喜劇，超越80年代經典喜劇《Cheers》保持多年的紀錄。<br />\n2007年啟播的《囧男大爆炸》播足12年，將科學帶到日常生活，一直深受觀眾歡迎，多位主要演員的片酬亦升至100萬美元（約780萬港元）一集，躋身史上最高薪電視演員之列，可惜有傳飾演靈魂人物Sheldon的Jim Parsons嫌被角色定型，決意辭演，令劇集在12季劃上句號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553837601_baba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553837601_baba.jpg&h=edd8f580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇集2007年開播。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553837601_1285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553837601_1285.jpg&h=68b7453a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年5月將播出最後一集。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190329/59425814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59425814&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HX%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=cf6d0a11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59425814&h=085e0d78\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190329/59425814</a>"},{"pid":"72b518c2ba509716cc242fb9baf9d18e82b242f2","tid":1082862,"uid":75610,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"睇到中後期已經冇睇"},{"pid":"6615417d2658e2b68bc15bbe6dc016537200a839","tid":1082862,"uid":49853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"拍一集可以買一層樓"},{"pid":"a16f08076af8428b9c65939eeae52e228fceca43","tid":1082862,"uid":149487,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:36:14.000Z","msg":"雖然好多人話後期唔好睇 放棄咗<br />\n但我仍然係死忠<br />\n好唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27da6e03e94831056be49eb120c9b9697de95292","tid":1082862,"uid":204531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72b518c2ba509716cc242fb9baf9d18e82b242f2","tid":1082862,"uid":75610,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"睇到中後期已經冇睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"Same 後期睇到笑都笑唔出"},{"pid":"3c1af5932147ccb3756b1955e6fce809e9231aed","tid":1082862,"uid":5077,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"27da6e03e94831056be49eb120c9b9697de95292","tid":1082862,"uid":204531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72b518c2ba509716cc242fb9baf9d18e82b242f2","tid":1082862,"uid":75610,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"睇到中後期已經冇睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"Same 後期睇到笑都笑唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"Amy整柒咗套劇"},{"pid":"34ed9078691ffb50a548f2bfea2259e15cb466bf","tid":1082862,"uid":60164,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3c1af5932147ccb3756b1955e6fce809e9231aed","tid":1082862,"uid":5077,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"27da6e03e94831056be49eb120c9b9697de95292","tid":1082862,"uid":204531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72b518c2ba509716cc242fb9baf9d18e82b242f2","tid":1082862,"uid":75610,"like":10,"dislike":1,"